When a decision gate fails (per README §7), write a postmortem here.

Template: YYYY-MM-DD-{gate-name}.md

# Gate failed: {what} on {date}

## Target vs actual

- Target: {from README §7}
- Actual: {real number}
- Gap: {how far off}

## What I tried

- Specific tactics, dates, channels

## Why I think it didn't work

- Three honest hypotheses, ordered by likelihood

## Decision

- [ ] Pivot the motion (try X instead of Y)
- [ ] Halt and reassess strategy
- [ ] (Specifically not: extend the deadline without changing approach)

## What I'm changing

- Concrete actions for next 30 days
